<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="js" lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta content="width=device-width" name="viewport">
  <title>Home | MyService</title>
  <link href="docs/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">

</head>
<body class="uikit-body uikit-grid landing-page uikit-refactor">
  <noscript><p role="alert">This website needs JavaScript to work properly.</p></noscript>
  <nav class="uikit-skip-link"><a class="uikit-skip-link__link" href="#main-content">Skip to main content</a></nav>
  <% include ../global/partials/header-version.ejs %>
  <% include header-landing-page.ejs %>
  <main>

    <section class="hero-main">
      <div class="container" id="main-content">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-8">
          <h1>An easier way to claim</h1>
          <p>If you are a current or former ADF member who enlisted after <strong>30 June 2004</strong>, try our new claims process.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4 ready-to-register">
          <button class="uikit-btn" onclick="window.location.href = '/register-step1'">Register</button> or <a href="#" class="panel-btn"><strong>Log&nbsp;in</strong></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container">
      <h2>Who can use MyService</h2>
      <p>For now, you can only use MyService if you enlisted in the ADF after 30 June 2004. We will open MyService to a wider group in the furture.</p>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-8">
          <section class="numbered-steps">
            <h2>How it works</h2>
            <ol>
              <li>
                <span class="numbers number-1"></span>
                <span class="numbered-steps-content">
                  <h3>Register with MyService</h3>
                  <p>Registrations are approved within 1 business day.</p>
                </span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="numbers number-2"></span>
                <span class="numbered-steps-content">
                  <h3>Make a claim</h3>
                  <p>Upload your medical diagnosis. If you do not have one, ask your GP or specialist to <a href="#">download and complete a diagnosis form (128KB PDF).</a></p>
                  <p>You do not need a diagnosis for mental health treatment.</p>
                </span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="numbers number-3"></span>
                <span class="numbered-steps-content">
                  <h3>Submit your claim</h3>
                  <p>If we need more information, we will let you know.</p>
                </span>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </section>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
          <section class="uikit-callout what-you-need">
            <h2>What you need</h2>
            <ul>
              <li class="ico-key">Your PMKeyS number</li>
              <li class="ico-calendar">Date of enlistment</li>
              <li class="ico-card">Your current driver's licence or Medicare card</li>
              <li class="ico-docs">A medical diagnosis and any supporting documents</li>
            </ul>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script src="/docs/js/jquery-3.2.1.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/docs/js/main.js"></script>
  <% include ../global/partials/footer.ejs %>
  <% include user/partials/panel-login.ejs %>



</body>
</html>
